### General Principles

- **Clean** - Readable, well-formatted code
- **Modular** - Organized into logical modules
- **Comment complex calculations** - Explain mathematical formulas
- **Suggest structural improvements when appropriate** - Help improve architecture
- **Avoid duplication** - Extract common functionality
- **Prioritize maintainability and scalability** - Balance simplicity with growth

