### Stat Calculator Pattern

```php
// /classes/Service/StatCalculator.php
namespace Game\Service;

class StatCalculator {
    /**
     * Calculate final combat stats
     * Order: Base → Realm → Blessings → Territory → Global → Era
     */
    public function calculateFinalStats(int $userId): array {
        $base = $this->getBaseStats($userId);
        $realm = $this->applyRealmMultipliers($base, $userId);
        $blessings = $this->applyBlessings($realm, $userId);
        $territory = $this->applyTerritoryBonus($blessings, $userId);
        $global = $this->applyGlobalInfluence($territory, $userId);
        $era = $this->applyEraModifiers($global, $userId);
        return $era;
    }
}
```

